      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid properties) documented and matched to simulation boundary conditions within stated uncertainty bands.",
      "rationale": "All five flow-speed operating points replicated in bench-top loop with glycerol-water blood analogue. Measured flow rates within ±2% of target; rotational speed within ±0.5%. Fluid viscosity and density characterised at test temperature and applied directly as CFD boundary conditions."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
