    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were scoped out as not required at MRL 2. The team concluded that the model provides High assurance for its intended use based on the breadth of validation activities, satisfactory output comparison (RMSE 9.8%), and direct relevance of QoI to the regulatory criterion. The discretization error GCI of 12.3% was noted but considered acceptable given the relative comparison framework. Assurance level declared High and decision outcome Accepted.",
